Name: Ca122
Sentence: A high T c exceeding 40 K was reported for lanthanoid-doped Ca122 single crystals by several groups , which exceeds the generally accepted highest T c of the AE122 systems of 38 K recorded by K-doped BaFe As 2 (Ba122) .

Among the AE122 systems, CaFe 2 As 2 (Ca122) is gathering considerable attention because of the recent increase in T c .
